{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"g-frontend","type":"group","x":-1300,"y":-1300,"width":850,"height":1180,"color":"6","label":"FRONTEND — Next.js 16 på Vercel"},
		{"id":"g-backend","type":"group","x":-400,"y":-1300,"width":850,"height":1180,"color":"5","label":"BACKEND — API-ruter + Edge Functions"},
		{"id":"g-data","type":"group","x":500,"y":-1300,"width":800,"height":1180,"color":"4","label":"DATA — Supabase (mdevyscqhpaogvsblfyp)"},
		{"id":"g-prompt","type":"group","x":-1300,"y":-60,"width":2600,"height":380,"color":"3","label":"PROMPT-WORKFLOW — Obsidian → Supabase → Gemini"},
		{"id":"g-config","type":"group","x":-1300,"y":380,"width":1300,"height":360,"color":"1","label":"KONFIGURATION & SECRETS"},
		{"id":"g-deploy","type":"group","x":50,"y":380,"width":1250,"height":360,"color":"2","label":"DEPLOYMENT & WORKFLOW"},

		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# 🌱 SPRING MARKETING NEWS — Tech Stack\n**Live:** spring-marketing-news.vercel.app · **Repo (personlig):** github.com/Farveblind5000/spring-marketing-news · **Repo (Spring Family IT):** github.com/Spring-Family-IT/Spring-Marketing-News · **Maj 2026 (post-Sprint 5)**","x":-1300,"y":-1480,"width":2600,"height":160},

		{"id":"fe-routes-header","type":"text","text":"## Routes (App Router · Server Components)","x":-1280,"y":-1280,"width":810,"height":40},
		{"id":"page-feed","type":"text","text":"### `/` — Feed\n`app/page.tsx`\n• 30-dages vindue (`scraped_at`)\n• Split: Denne uge / Ældre uger\n• Filter-tabs: Alle / AI / Marketing / ⚡ Opsummerede (URL `?filter=`)","x":-1280,"y":-1230,"width":390,"height":160,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"page-saved","type":"text","text":"### `/saved` — Gemte\n`app/saved/page.tsx`\nKræver login · viser brugerens gemte artikler · two-query pattern","x":-870,"y":-1230,"width":390,"height":160,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"page-digest","type":"text","text":"### `/digest` — Personligt digest\n`app/digest/page.tsx`\n• Læser `user_digest_queue`\n• Viser unified-rapport ØVERST (hvis genereret)\n• Liste af valgte artikler nedenfor","x":-1280,"y":-1060,"width":390,"height":160,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"page-login","type":"text","text":"### `/login` — Login\n`app/login/page.tsx`\nEmail + password (Supabase Auth)\nManuel oprettelse i dashboard","x":-870,"y":-1060,"width":390,"height":160,"color":"6"},

		{"id":"fe-components-header","type":"text","text":"## Client Components (`app/components/`)","x":-1280,"y":-880,"width":810,"height":40},
		{"id":"comp-articlecard","type":"text","text":"### ArticleCard\n`ArticleCard.tsx`\nSamler alle artikel-aktioner: gem, send-til-digest, kort opsummering (⚡ ekspanderbar). `defaultExpanded` når filter=summarized.","x":-1280,"y":-830,"width":390,"height":170,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"comp-actions","type":"text","text":"### Action-knapper\n• `SaveButton` — bookmark toggle\n• `SendToDigestButton` — write til `user_digest_queue`\n• `GenerateDigestButton` — POST /api/generate-digest\n• `GenerateUnifiedButton` — POST /api/generate-unified","x":-870,"y":-830,"width":390,"height":170,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"comp-editable","type":"text","text":"### EditableUnifiedReport\n`EditableUnifiedReport.tsx`\nView/edit-modes for AI-rapporten. Tekst-felter for theme/context/insights/trends/sources. Gem → POST /api/update-unified.","x":-1280,"y":-650,"width":390,"height":170,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"comp-export","type":"text","text":"### ExportButton + UnifiedReportPDF\n• `ExportButton.tsx` — dropdown PDF/email\n• `UnifiedReportPDF.tsx` — `@react-pdf/renderer` template (1-side A4 + artikel-kort på side 2+)\nBrand: \"EMILS AI NEWS\"","x":-870,"y":-650,"width":390,"height":170,"color":"6"},

		{"id":"fe-libstyle-header","type":"text","text":"## Lib + styling","x":-1280,"y":-470,"width":810,"height":40},
		{"id":"lib-supabase","type":"text","text":"### `lib/supabase/`\n• `server.ts` — Server-side klient (cookies via @supabase/ssr)\n• `client.ts` — Browser-side klient\nBegge bruger anon key fra `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`","x":-1280,"y":-420,"width":810,"height":140,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"styling","type":"text","text":"### Styling\n`app/globals.css` · Tailwind v4 + brand-tokens\n`--orange: #FF3700` · `--offblack: #1A1A1A` · `--gunmetal: #484848` · `--bg: #F4F4F4`\nFont: DM Sans (Google Fonts)","x":-1280,"y":-260,"width":810,"height":130,"color":"6"},

		{"id":"be-api-header","type":"text","text":"## Next.js API-ruter (`app/api/*`)","x":-380,"y":-1280,"width":810,"height":40},
		{"id":"api-generate-digest","type":"text","text":"### `/api/generate-digest`\nGenererer personligt digest fra `user_digest_queue` + valgt prompt-template fra `settings.digest_prompt`. Output-format ART_N_TITLE/SOURCE/SUMMARY/TAKEAWAY1-3.","x":-380,"y":-1230,"width":390,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"api-generate-unified","type":"text","text":"### `/api/generate-unified`\nKonsoliderer digest til struktureret briefing (THEME/CONTEXT/KEY_INSIGHTS/TRENDS/SOURCES). Bruger `unified_output_prompt`. Token-cap: 3000+200·N (max 6000).","x":10,"y":-1230,"width":390,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"api-update-unified","type":"text","text":"### `/api/update-unified`\nGemmer manuel redigering af unified-rapport. Bevarer `unified_generated_at` (AI-timestamp).","x":-380,"y":-1060,"width":390,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"api-short-summary","type":"text","text":"### `/api/short-summary`\nKalder Gemini for én artikel · check global cache (`articles.short_summary`) først. Format: 1 intro-linje + 3-4 bullets + målgruppe-tag.","x":10,"y":-1060,"width":390,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"api-export-pdf","type":"text","text":"### `/api/export-pdf`\nRenderer `UnifiedReportPDF` til PDF stream via `@react-pdf/renderer`. Filename: `emils-ai-news-uge-X-YYYY.pdf`.","x":-380,"y":-890,"width":390,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"api-export-email","type":"text","text":"### `/api/export-email`\nResend API · HTML body + PDF attached. FROM: onboarding@resend.dev · default recipient = login-email · `RESEND_API_KEY` påkrævet.","x":10,"y":-890,"width":390,"height":160,"color":"5"},

		{"id":"be-edge-header","type":"text","text":"## Supabase Edge Functions (Deno)","x":-380,"y":-700,"width":810,"height":40},
		{"id":"edge-scrape","type":"text","text":"### `scrape-articles`\n`supabase/functions/scrape-articles/index.ts`\n1. Læs `sources` (active=true)\n2. `npm:rss-parser@3` parser feeds\n3. Dedup på URL\n4. Indsæt i `articles`\n5. Kald Gemini → summary + relevance_score","x":-380,"y":-650,"width":390,"height":190,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"edge-digest","type":"text","text":"### `generate-digest` _(legacy)_\n`supabase/functions/generate-digest/index.ts`\n**IKKE i brug.** Globalt digest erstattet af personligt Next.js API (2026-05-04).","x":10,"y":-650,"width":390,"height":190,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"cron","type":"text","text":"### pg_cron + pg_net (Supabase)\n• `daglig-scraper` — `0 4 * * *` (06:00 dansk) → POST `scrape-articles`\n• `ugentlig-digest` — `0 18 * * 0` _(deaktiveret)_\nKonfigureret manuelt via SQL Editor.","x":-380,"y":-450,"width":810,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"sync-script","type":"text","text":"### `scripts/sync-prompt.js`\nNode.js CLI · `node scripts/sync-prompt.js`\nLæser ALLE filer i `01_docs/Prompts/` (Digest + Short Summary + Unified Output) · upsert til Supabase `settings`-tabel via service_role key.","x":-380,"y":-280,"width":810,"height":160,"color":"5"},

		{"id":"data-auth","type":"text","text":"### Supabase Auth\nEmail + password · session via cookies (`@supabase/ssr`)\n3 brugere oprettet · manuel email-bekræftelse i SQL","x":520,"y":-1280,"width":760,"height":110,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"data-tables-header","type":"text","text":"## DB-tabeller","x":520,"y":-1160,"width":760,"height":40},
		{"id":"tbl-sources","type":"text","text":"### sources\nRSS-feeds · `name, feed_url, topic, active, last_scraped`\n4 aktive kilder","x":520,"y":-1110,"width":370,"height":120,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"tbl-articles","type":"text","text":"### articles\n`title, url, summary, full_content, topic, relevance_score, read_time_min, scraped_at, source_id`\n**+ short_summary, short_summary_generated_at** (cache)","x":910,"y":-1110,"width":370,"height":160,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"tbl-saves","type":"text","text":"### user_saves\n`user_id, article_id, created_at`\nBookmark — gem til senere","x":520,"y":-940,"width":370,"height":120,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"tbl-queue","type":"text","text":"### user_digest_queue ⭐\n`user_id, article_id, added_at`\nEksplicit valg til næste digest (Sprint 5)","x":910,"y":-940,"width":370,"height":120,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"tbl-digests","type":"text","text":"### digests\n`user_id, week_number, year, content (JSON), article_count, source_count, created_at`\n**+ unified_content, unified_generated_at**","x":520,"y":-810,"width":760,"height":140,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"tbl-settings","type":"text","text":"### settings\n`key (PK), content, updated_at` · RLS: read public\nKeys: `digest_prompt`, `short_summary_prompt`, `unified_output_prompt` (drives af Obsidian)","x":520,"y":-660,"width":760,"height":130,"color":"4"},

		{"id":"ext-header","type":"text","text":"## Eksterne services","x":520,"y":-520,"width":760,"height":40},
		{"id":"ext-gemini","type":"text","text":"### 🤖 Gemini 2.5 Flash\nEndpoint: `v1/models/gemini-2.5-flash:generateContent`\nBruges af: scrape-articles, /api/generate-digest, /api/generate-unified, /api/short-summary\nThinking-tokens-buffer indregnet i `maxOutputTokens`.","x":520,"y":-470,"width":760,"height":160,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"ext-resend","type":"text","text":"### 📧 Resend (email)\nGratis 100/dag · FROM: `onboarding@resend.dev`\nBruges af: /api/export-email","x":520,"y":-300,"width":370,"height":110,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"ext-rss","type":"text","text":"### 📡 RSS-kilder\nTechCrunch AI · VentureBeat AI · HubSpot Marketing · Moz Blog\n(styres via `sources`-tabellen)","x":910,"y":-300,"width":370,"height":110,"color":"2"},

		{"id":"obsidian-prompts","type":"text","text":"### 📓 Obsidian: 3 prompts\n`01_docs/Prompts/`\n• `Digest System Prompt.md`\n• `Short Summary Prompt.md`\n• `Unified Output Prompt.md`\n\nFrontmatter `settings_key:` styrer hvor de lander i Supabase.","x":-1280,"y":0,"width":500,"height":290,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"sync-flow","type":"text","text":"### ⚙️ Sync-script\n`node scripts/sync-prompt.js`\n\n1. Loop over filer i `Prompts/`\n2. Læs frontmatter `settings_key`\n3. Strip metadata\n4. Upsert til `settings.<key>`\n\n_Kræver `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`_","x":-740,"y":0,"width":480,"height":290,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"settings-fetch","type":"text","text":"### 🗄️ settings-tabel\nSupabase row pr. prompt\n\nHentet af relevant API-rute ved hvert kald (ingen cache)\n\n**Fallback:** hardkodet prompt i route hvis row mangler","x":-220,"y":0,"width":420,"height":290,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"gemini-call","type":"text","text":"### 🤖 Gemini-kald\nVariabel-substitution → POST til Gemini 2.5 Flash\n\n`temperature: 0.3`\n`maxOutputTokens` tunet pr. rute (thinking-buffer)\n\nServer-side parser KEY:value-format → typed objekter","x":240,"y":0,"width":480,"height":290,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"render","type":"text","text":"### 🖥️ Render\nServer Component fetcher fra DB → render i UI\n\n• `/digest` — unified + artikel-kort\n• `/` — short_summary i ArticleCard\n• `/digest` PDF/email export","x":760,"y":0,"width":520,"height":290,"color":"3"},

		{"id":"env-local","type":"text","text":"### `.env.local` (lokal · gitignored)\n```\nNEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL\nNEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY\nSUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY\nGEMINI_API_KEY\nRESEND_API_KEY\n```\nBruges af Next.js dev + sync-script","x":-1280,"y":420,"width":410,"height":290,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"vercel-env","type":"text","text":"### Vercel Env Vars (production)\n```\nNEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL\nNEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY\nGEMINI_API_KEY\nRESEND_API_KEY\n```\nSat via `vercel env add ... production`\nKræver redeploy ved ændring.","x":-850,"y":420,"width":410,"height":290,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"supabase-secrets","type":"text","text":"### Supabase Secrets (Edge Functions)\n```\nGEMINI_API_KEY\nSUPABASE_URL\nSUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY\n```\nAuto-tilgængelige i Deno via `Deno.env.get()`","x":-420,"y":420,"width":390,"height":290,"color":"1"},

		{"id":"deploy-frontend","type":"text","text":"### Frontend deploy\nGit remotes:\n• `origin` → personligt repo\n• `spring` → Spring Family IT (fælles)\n\n```\ngit push origin main\ngit push spring main\nvercel --prod\n```\n\nVercel auto-deploy kobles til ét repo.","x":80,"y":420,"width":390,"height":290,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"deploy-edge","type":"text","text":"### Edge Function deploy\n```\n./supabase-cli/supabase.exe \\\n  functions deploy <navn> \\\n  --project-ref mdevyscqhpaogvsblfyp\n```\nWindows: binary i `./supabase-cli/`\n_(ikke npm)_","x":490,"y":420,"width":390,"height":290,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"deploy-prompt","type":"text","text":"### Prompt-opdatering\n1. Rediger `01_docs/Prompts/<navn>.md`\n2. `node scripts/sync-prompt.js`\n3. Næste API-kald bruger ny prompt\n\n**Ingen redeploy nødvendig** — prompt læses ved hvert kald.","x":900,"y":420,"width":390,"height":290,"color":"2"},

		{"id":"tldr","type":"text","text":"## 🚀 TL;DR — Hurtig orientering for ny samarbejdspartner\n\n| Fil | Formål |\n|---|---|\n| `app/page.tsx` | Feed-siden — entry point + filter + uge-split |\n| `app/digest/page.tsx` | Digest-siden — viser unified-rapport + valgte artikler |\n| `app/components/ArticleCard.tsx` | Samler alle artikel-aktioner i ét sted |\n| `app/api/generate-unified/route.ts` | Konsoliderer digest til struktureret briefing |\n| `app/api/short-summary/route.ts` | LLM-extract pr. artikel + global cache |\n| `app/api/export-pdf/route.tsx` + `export-email/route.tsx` | PDF/email via @react-pdf/renderer + Resend |\n| `supabase/functions/scrape-articles/index.ts` | Daglig RSS-scraper (pg_cron 06:00) |\n| `01_docs/Prompts/*.md` | Levende prompts — synces til Supabase via `sync-prompt.js` |\n| `01_docs/Plan/Roadmap.md` | Sprint-status + arkitektur-beslutninger |\n| `01_docs/CHANGELOG.md` | Append-only log over alle ændringer |\n| `CLAUDE.md` | Projektkontekst til Claude Code-sessioner |","x":-1300,"y":770,"width":2600,"height":320}
	],
